Package: pbbamr
Type: Package
Title: Interface R with PacBio BAM File Formats
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-12-09
Author: Nigel Delaney
Maintainer: Nigel Delaney <google.can.find.me@somewhere.net>
Description: This R package wraps both the pbbam and htslib libraries, providing
    tools to query and investigate BAM files taking advantage of the PBI index
    format.
